 Carolina, South Carolina and Virginia. Please be prepared, be careful and be SAFE!</p>\r\n<div class=\"Tweet-metadata dateline\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #697882; margin-top: 3.2px;\"><a class=\"u-linkBlend u-url customisable-highlight long-permalink\" style=\"background-color: transparent; text-decoration: inherit; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit;\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1039291783031734273\" data-datetime=\"2018-09-10T23:17:24+0000\" data-scribe=\"element:full_timestamp\">4:47 AM - Sep 11, 2018</a></div>\r\n<ul class=\"Tweet-actions Tweet-action--newsActions\" style=\"margin: 8.4px 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: none; display: flex; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden;\" role=\"menu\" data-scribe=\"component:actions\" aria-label=\"Tweet actions\">\r\n<li class=\"Tweet-action Tweet-action--newsAction\" style=\"display: inline-block;\">\r\n<div class=\"Icon Icon--heartEdge TweetAction-icon\" style=\"display: inline-block; height: 1.25em; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; vertical-align: text-bottom; width: 1.25em; flex-shrink: 0;\" role=\"img\" data-scribe=\"element:heart\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<a class=\"Tweet-action--heart TweetAction TweetAction--heartEdge\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: #697882; text-decoration-line: none; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; outline: 0px;\" title=\"Like\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/like?tweet_id=1039291783031734273\" data-scribe=\"component:actions\"><span class=\"TweetAction-stat\" style=\"display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: text-bottom; margin-left: 3px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; min-width: 0px;\" data-scribe=\"element:heart_count\">73.9K</span></a></li>\r\n<li class=\"Tweet-action Tweet-action--newsAction\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 7px; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div class=\"Icon Icon--replyEdge TweetAction-icon\" style=\"display: inline-block;